        <li>Text-to-speech and speech-to-text capabilities</li>
        <li>Configurable AI personas with customizable behavior</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        The Service acts as an <strong>intermediary layer</strong> between the user and third-party AI models.
        OpenOcto does not independently generate AI responses -- all AI-generated content originates from
        the configured third-party AI backends.
